<div id="stitle" style="display:none;">Letter</div>
<div class="nbunit" id="21Oct1934"><font color="red">21 October 1934</font> <i>Letters I</i> (to Harriet Weaver): L&eacute;on managed to get leave from the French to come here for 3 days &hellip; [letter from Lucia] was sent on the 30th anniversary of my first marriage &hellip; if you can get from the London library a copy of the life of Nijinsky by his wife in English and read it, especially the appendix you will get some idea of the danger that is feared </div>
